Being a compendium of the facts major and minor known about the planet
Ea.(AAA-Yaa) 
 
^BThe Universe:^b  
     More correctly called the multiverse. There is a large number of
planes related to the plane of interest called the prime material plane.  

^BThe Solar system:^b
     The star is a single sun of the white dwarf form. There are three
moons in near circular orbits. None of the moons can support life. The
moons are Litaha,Yrtha,Yamen. 
 
^BThe World of Ea:^b
     The world itself is a heavy grav planet with G=1.7 times that of Sol
III. The planet has 60% water coverage with one large continent and
several large islands. The year is 400 days(24 hrs) long with 40 10 day
weeks. There are 10 4 week months.
 
