^BThe Val-Tier:^b
     All of a Val-Tier's physical statistics are generated using the
procedure for Barbarians as described in Unearthed Arcana. The Average VT
is 8' plus or minus 11". The average weight is 260 lbs. They are a fairly
dark skinned (copper to bronze) race with light blonde hair. 7 % of all
women are platinum blonde( Y-linked recessive). They have a high
resistance to alcohol and are well adapted to heights. 
 
^BThe Grey Elves:^b
     The Gray elves are a race that is not native to Ea . The are, on
average, 6'2" and 165 Lbs. Their hair varies from Blond to platinum blond
in color. Their eyes go from Violet to Silver. They gain a +1 INT +1 CHA
-2 CON  +1 Proficiency in Longsword +1 Proficiency in Longbow All Gray
Elves are psionic.  

^BThe Sulimane:^b
     Commonly known as the Ghost Riders. They are a group of tribesmen
from another plane. They are strong and fast +1 Strength,+1 Dexterity yet
they are adversely affected by the atmosphere(low oxygen) -2 to
Constitution. They are black skinned with a high density low bulk
muscalature giving them the appearence of skeletons. Their eyes flouresce
even in the weak ultraviolet of night. They are almost exclusively night 
dwellers.

^BThe Uru:^b
     The Uru are also known as the black dwarves. They fit that
description with their ebony skin and dark brown eyes. They are strong and
tough giving a +1 Strength and +1 Constitution with minimums of str:15 and
con:15 and they are much less than charismatic at a -2 to Charisma. They
average the same in height and weight as a normal dwarf.  .1% of all uru
have the blue eyes that mark the born leader of the Uru nation. The Uru
have a 100% magic resistance that prevents them from being affected by or
using persona based magic. Only a druid may directly affect them with
spells of less than 6th level.

.bp
^BHigh Elves:^b
     High elves fit the character race description found in the PH except
that high elves gain a +1 charisma, -1 Con. They are light skinned with
brown hair and green eyes. some 10% of all high elves display a set of
yellow eyes.
 
^BWood Elves :^b
     Wood elves gain a +1 to dexterity and -1 to constitution. Their
appearence is as High elves though 30% are found to have yellow eyes. 
 
^BDrow Elves:^b
     The Drow are a race of elves that spend their time as underground
dwellers. They are sensitive to the light and bright light or sunlight
reduces their dexterity by 2 and all their saves are at a -2 for the
duration. Fairy fire and other lower intensity sources reduce dexterity by
one and all attacks are at a -1.
     Their skin is a deep black that contains almost no melanin. They have
either white or silver hair and black eyes. Drow do not have the +1  for
bow and longsword. Instead they may attack with two weapons without
penalty with the following restriction: each weapon must be a W.O.P. 
     Drowspeak the languages of the underground in much the same way as
gnomes. Also they have their own private toungue which is a hand speech or
finger talk. Their vision is inravision for 60 ' and they have the normal
charm resistance and find concealed percentages. 

^BCentaur:^b
     Centaurs gain a +2 Con and a -2 Charisma. They gain a +1/+1 when
using bows and a -2 using any bladed weapon. Centaurs of a healer family
are +1 con and -1 Cha. Centaurs prefer short bows or wheel bows. 
 
^BGnomes:^b
     The gnomes of Ea are scarce and rarely seen. They tend to be coloured
similiar to dwarves and have gem like eyes. Otherwise they conform in all
ways to the PH description. 
 
^BKorobokuru:^b
     The Korobokuru is a gnome variant found in the Eastern islands. They
gain a +1 STR +1 Con and -2 Int. These additions must allow the PC to make
racial minimums. This race conforms to the description found in the
Oriental Adventures.

.bp
^BDwarves:^b
     Dwarves are short stout thick skulled . They gain a +1 to Con and a
-1 to Charisma. 
 
^BHalflings:^b
     They tend to have human coloring and are quite lazy. They gain a +1
to Dex and a -1 to Str. 
 
^BHengeyokai:^b
     These are animal folk whose features and statistics are dependent
upon their animal form ( see OA ) . 
 
^BShapeChanger(2%):^b
     Shapechangers are similiar to Hengeyokai with some exceptions. They
have only a animal form and human form. They are dependent upon the moons 
changes for their shapechange. They may only be hit by silver or +1
weapons in animal form. They are affected by all magics affecting
lycanthropes. 

^Bhalf-elves:Half-Orcs:^b
     Though they are not a unique race these two types of humanoids often
have a profound effect upon the world. 
 
^BSilkie:^b
     Also called the Acha Sidhe . The Silkie are a race of aquatic half
elf/shape changers or Wereseals . There statistics are as half elves
except in animal form.  

